# Salvage Specialist SOP

[bold]1.[/bold] Salvage Specialists are [bold]not[/bold] permitted to hoard materials. All mined materials are to be left in the Ore Processor;

[bold]2.[/bold] Salvage Specialists are [bold]not[/bold] permitted to throw people into manufactured wormholes, nor are they permitted to trick people into using Bluespace Crystals, or throwing Bluespace Crystals at anyone;

[bold]3.[/bold] Salvage Specialists are [bold]not[/bold] permitted to give expedition acquired items to station crew, unless the [color=#1b67a5]Quartermaster[/color] approves;

[bold]4.[/bold] Salvage Specialists are bound by guidelines set for [color=#b18644]Cargo Technicians[/color] when inside the Cargo Office or Bay;
